author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Bruise Violet, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2015.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Maybe You’re the Problem
00:02:42 Sketchy Jeff
00:05:50 Wasted

Musicians
Emily Schoonover — vocals, guitar
Bella Dawson — bass, vocals
Emily Cusack — drums, vocals

Credits
Engineer – Michael DeMark
Producer – David Campbell
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.

author: The Current
description:
Gary Louris performs "Listening To Bobby Charles" from 'Dark Country'
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Best known for his work as the frontman of the longtime indie-rock band The Jayhawks, singer-songwriter Gary Louris released 'Dark Country,' his fourth solo album, on February 14, 2025.

Watch a performance of "Listening To Bobby Charles" above.

Musician
Gary Louris – vocals, guitar
